{"tid":1345780,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"於港鐵元朗站外追問警察為何未有及時趕抵元朗站","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:31.000Z","uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f743497828c42ab1e8d65165eecdb166643cf0f","tid":1345780,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【警員指不知收Call時間】有記者於近凌晨十二時，於港鐵元朗站外追問警察為何未有及時趕抵元朗站，阻止混亂發生。一名自稱是八鄉分區指揮官李漢民的警員指，自己收到報案時「無睇錶」，所以不知道當時是幾點，又要求記者不要質問他，並指記者問問題不會令他害怕。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #元朗襲擊</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2680847252023314?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2680847252023314%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=8fcd9624\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2680847252023314?sfns=mo</a>"}]}